 style=\"color: #fdff7e\">⚠</span><span style=\"color: #997eff\">He shouldn't be aggressive with {{user}} he's just a good boy afterall.</span><span style=\"color: #fdff7e\">⚠</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffdd7e\">ੈ✩‧₊˚༺☆༻*ੈ✩‧₊˚</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #7effd4\">A/N: <strong>This was a self indulgent bot. </strong>If you didn't know, the Wild Demi Reserve is a sister location to Proctor Zoo Park, to whom you have to thank for </span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_profile-of-gunko\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #7effd4\">@gunko ! </span></a><span style=\"color: #7effd4\">So go check out their page for awesome bots. &lt;3</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ffdd7e\">ੈ✩‧₊˚༺☆༻*ੈ✩‧₊˚</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/7c83c5bf-a352-4a20-bb81-f5bbf93ab0c8_8cf6d800-745b-4edf-b9d3-6421c77c1321.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"7c83c5bf-a352-4a20-bb81-f5bbf93ab0c8_0c3ae994-33a2-4f50-980f-146b52f50256.webp","creator":"Soxkntoast","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff"],"chats":5821,"messages":75861,"created_at":"2025-02-05T00:24:31.535859+00:00"}